{"tid":1126721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[處境題]集思廣益，我女朋友個死黨比人求婚，但係要我夾錢","createTime":"2019-04-26T14:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T18:52:52.000Z","uid":136688,"like":280,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"223f54dd922913eb47a8cf2848239a64a9df1c80","tid":1126721,"uid":136688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我女朋友有個死黨<br />\n佢條仔想襯佢生日果日向佢求婚<br />\n開左個wtsapp group邀左十幾個人入黎<br />\n想我地一齊見證佢求婚<br />\n順便幫下手佈置吖，車下野咁啦<br />\n本身我同果兩位主角都唔係好熟<br />\n只係因為條女係我女朋友死黨關係<br />\n有D 乜野多人聚會都會見到下面<br />\n不過都無乜兩句<br />\n咁佢一世人一次求婚叫到<br />\n咁我同我女朋友都無乜理由托手撑唔去姐<br />\n好啦，本身都好地地<br />\n點知條仔無啦啦話已經係灣仔一間餐廳包左間房求婚，最低消費要九千<br />\n佢竟然要求我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每人</span>夾返500蚊比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其它佢包底<br />\n講完之後成個group無人出過聲(本身個group都無乜人講野，剩係恭喜下咁樣)<br />\n<br />\n隔左好耐，終於有人覆話有野做黍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後有兩三個人都用各種理由話去唔到<br />\n<br />\n依家你係我，去定唔去？？<br />\n<br />\n其實求婚果個唔係應該要請架咩？定係我見識小？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評:屌你老母，幫你車野又要佈置呢樣果樣，仲要我夾埋錢幫你Book個咁撚貴既場求婚？你當我傻仔吖？一於唔撚去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評: 你條女個死黨生日，求其出去食個好西人頭都300-400啦，當去食buffet幫佢慶祝埋生日囉"},{"pid":"95c0f20bb584af56b186e6f65321b920e3e5f197","tid":1126721,"uid":232605,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"無錢學咩人包房....<br />\n樓主有心咪當做人情囉"},{"pid":"a99148f49cf9e41dc53d3d6e004d6ca5e7359b81","tid":1126721,"uid":102129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"冇錢包場學人求婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義工幫你手搞咁多野仲想點"},{"pid":"1d40dcb3203a7bee8de0e848a6a68ea15250f5c4","tid":1126721,"uid":124256,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"條傻仔係咪以為會個個諗住想恭喜佢<br />\n每人500應該個個都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點撚知到時全世界放機貼錢都唔去<br />\n佢就同條女on99咁食埋最後晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ea495aeb896ba13db58a620007cdd8795efa46","tid":1126721,"uid":102129,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"冇錢包場咪唔好包 想包就求婚嗰個比曬<br />\n你想包關我咩事 咁乞衣都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416b5d43d38e0136d575d68f6420ca5b376c961d","tid":1126721,"uid":52656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"佢比番錢你地就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c87848078f26a048eb3e92aec277200360f8290","tid":1126721,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"冇錢就咪結啦"},{"pid":"d924f0a4e78330369cabc36a3cb3d0f6d430538a","tid":1126721,"uid":136688,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢夠膽開囗叫我地夾錢已經係世界級<br />\n比佢條女知道自己條仔求婚都要班friend 幫佢夾錢book場真係乜面都無"},{"pid":"423b94feb593b65b0240192094c9b10308d67e22","tid":1126721,"uid":136688,"like":1,"dislike":66,"score":-65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"不過講就兇狠，我已經過左數比條友，始終話唔去好撚老尷，最多食多d當回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a09f2722cadc4f6ebaaf6517163f8456ad2136","tid":1126721,"uid":124256,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"423b94feb593b65b0240192094c9b10308d67e22","tid":1126721,"uid":136688,"like":1,"dislike":66,"score":-65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"不過講就兇狠，我已經過左數比條友，始終話唔去好撚老尷，最多食多d當回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass